This paper deals with differentially private algorithms, which are commonly used in the field of cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, the paper also discusses the application of these algorithms in machine learning (cs.LG) and data analysis (cs.DS). The paper also involves the use of information theory (cs.IT) in developing the algorithms. Finally, the paper discusses the selection problem, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
